content:
How can outdoor activities impact the self-care practices of individuals with rare genetic disorders? Please provide a research paper exploring this topic.
Here is an example of the JSON data that could be included in the paper:
{
   "participants": "30 individuals with rare genetic disorders",
   "treatment": "participation in outdoor activities",
   "results": [
      {
         "metric": "reduction in pain",
         "change": "-20%"
      },
      {
         "metric": "improvement in mental health",
         "change": "+25%"
      },
      {
         "metric": "increase in socialization",
         "change": "+35%"
      }
   ],
   "conclusion": "Participation in outdoor activities for individuals with rare genetic disorders may lead to significant improvements in pain management, mental health, and socialization." 
}
